          "COVARIANCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Description of energy-energy correlation given by",
                " Mitja Majerle (2020-05-08):",
                "1. Peak area fitting:",
                " Correlation due to background subtraction exists,",
                " and even significant (~0.5) with (n,p) peaks.",
                "2. Collected proton charge:",
                " Fully correlated within 2011 data; uncorrelated for",
                " uncertainty higher than 5% for 2013 data; fully",
                " correlated with 2011 data for uncertainty equal to or",
                " lower than 5% for 2013.",
                "3. Number of 7Li nuclei in Li foil:",
                " Fully correlated within 2011 data; fully correlated",
                " within 2013 data; correlated between 2011 and 2013",
                " data (>0.5 is suggested)",
                "4. 7Li(p,n)7Be cross section:",
                " Fully correlated.",
                "5. Forwardness of peak neutrons:",
